{"tid":1369836,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"既然遍地開花 不如正式搞界別聯署","createTime":"2019-07-26T20:02:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T21:36:41.000Z","uid":148187,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9c5757ae7a29618c2b3a96e42ef20f6177523f1e","tid":1369836,"uid":148187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T20:02:42.000Z","msg":"其實遍地開花公開信嘅重點在於，畀人匿名發表「工會/我老細（政府）不代表我」嘅聲音。<br />\n<br />\n但係而家有啲界別聲音過於鬆散，演化到任何人三五成群都可以影自己張證就可以出信、重複出信，好似啲狗屌張建宗咁，變咗冇咩公信力。<br />\n<br />\n建議：接下嚟各個界別喺工會以外進行正正式式聯署（匿唔匿名也好），一來「不代表我」發聲更有力（總好過下款寫一群人然後淨係得十張證），二來畀大眾睇到嗰個界別發聲嘅確切人數成件事好睇啲咁。<br />\n<br />\n727元朗手足加油"},{"pid":"727630a0f9c519dbab4d60eeabd8324b143df1f6","tid":1369836,"uid":148187,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T20:03:12.000Z","msg":"而且聯署內容亦都可以跟返界別專業而異，例如港鐵將軍澳線車長們話要港鐵交代元朗站嘅處理，醫護界可以話橡膠子彈點樣死得人等等"},{"pid":"8fc39161d30446aa6fe0a1f264862a2559072a5f","tid":1369836,"uid":148187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T20:03:27.000Z","msg":"推畀未瞓嘅你睇"},{"pid":"138ce036f48eb5398495ae2974026bc3002898b0","tid":1369836,"uid":148187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T20:03:40.000Z","msg":"再嚟推"},{"pid":"cc321ba1796a38108951a733f43cb5b7975ab475","tid":1369836,"uid":148187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T20:04:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb4acd5c2969f2f455b7c6e8b401fcd2a8d5cbc","tid":1369836,"uid":148187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T20:05:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6374e71464bb3a9ea3f913f720fccb07167bae31","tid":1369836,"uid":148187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T20:07:55.000Z","msg":"我又推"},{"pid":"f6bb769a343f52cffbabce688f7144c27a59c6b0","tid":1369836,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T20:09:00.000Z","msg